{"lemma":"عَجِيبَةُ","slug":"عَجِيبَةُ","root":"ع.ج.ب","root_slug":"ع-ج-ب","root_link":"/words/roots/ع-ج-ب","pos":"ADJ","pos_camel":"adj","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"عَجِيب","root":"عجب","pos":"N","occurrence_count":2},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["adj"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":5},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n28104"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B9%D9%8E%D8%AC%D9%90%D9%8A%D8%A8%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"adj","gloss":"wonderful, marvelous"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"foreign"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"exotic"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"amazing"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"weird, strange"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/ʕa.d͡ʒiːb/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n28104","headword_ar":"عَجِيبَةٌ","root":"Ejb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"(K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^uEojuwbapN","text_ar":"اُعْجُوبَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A wonderful thing; a thing at which one wonders:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K: *) [the pl. of the former, accord. to modern usage, is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EajaAy^ibu","text_ar":"عَجَايِبُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", mentioned above as pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EajabN","text_ar":"عَجَبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": and]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aEaAjiybu","text_ar":"اَعَاجِيبُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"seems to be pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^uEojuwbapN","text_ar":"اُعْجُوبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", like as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aHaAdiyvu","text_ar":"اَحَادِيثُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^uHoduwvapu","text_ar":"اُحْدُوثَةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, O:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taEaAjiybu","text_ar":"تَعَاجِيبُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wonderful things;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EajaAy^ibu","text_ar":"عَجَايِبُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, O, K;) and is a word [of a rare form, (see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tabaA$iyru","text_ar":"تَبَاشِيرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":",)] having no proper sing., (S, O,) like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taEaA$iybu","text_ar":"تَعَاشِيبُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (O;) erroneously thought by the author of the “ Námoos ” [on the Kámoos] to be most probably a mistake for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aEaAjiybu","text_ar":"اَعَاجِيبُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) a poet says,"},{"kind":"quote","text":"wamano taEaAjiybi xaloqi A@ll~`hi gaATiyapN\n                      \n                     \n                        yuEoSaru minohaA mulaAHiY~N wagirobiybu"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And of the wonderful things of God's creation is a grape-vine covering the ground"},{"kind":"text","text":"(so"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gaATiyapN","text_ar":"غَاطِيَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is expl. by IB),"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"whereof grapes of the kinds called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mlAHY~","text_ar":"ملاحىّ"},{"kind":"page_break","n":1958},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"grbyb","text_ar":"غربيب"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"are pressed"},{"kind":"text","text":"for making wine]. (S, O.)"}],"source_refs":["K","S","O","TA"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}